::Battera::

She looked at the ground and decided to go to the hatch and look 
outside. She hadn't done that in a while and looking at the sky 
always cheered her up.  She turned and walked down the hallway.  She 
saw a bot run past her.  She kept going and went to the hatch.  She 
opened it and saw a bot standing there. "Oh, Hello there. Ah, can I 
help you?"
